sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant API as API Routes
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Browser: Click profile icon → "Edit Profile"
    Browser->>API: GET /api/users?userId={id}&reqType=profile
    API->>DB: User.findUnique(include: farms, gates, crops,<br/>livestock, equipment, emergencyNeeds)
    DB-->>API: Full user profile + all farm data
    API-->>Browser: Profile data
    Browser-->>User: Display profile with farm cards

    User->>Browser: Navigate through tabs to update information
    Browser->>API: PUT /api/users
    Note right of Browser: { name, phoneNumber, bio, emailNotifications }
    API->>DB: User.update(where: sessionUserId, data: fields)
    DB-->>API: Updated user
    API-->>Browser: 200 OK
    Browser-->>User: Click "Save Changes"
